data.description: Introducing your dream home in the heart of Virginia Beach with a first floor en suite that is absolutely stunning! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style property has been thoughtfully updated, boasting a fresh and modern interior that's sure to capture your heart. Step inside and be greeted by spacious, sunlit rooms for comfortable living. The heart of this home is the open-concept living area, with a stylishly remodeled kitchen and a cozy living room that invites you to relax and unwind. Sliding glass doors open to a generously-sized, fully fenced backyard, providing a private oasis for your outdoor enjoyment. Imagine summer barbecues, and your own garden retreat in this expansive, well-maintained space. This is more than just a house; it's the ideal home you've been searching for in beautiful Virginia Beach. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
